<p id="fs-idm868160">(a)<span data-type="newline"><br/></span></p><span data-type="media" id="fs-idm72846160" data-alt="Two Lewis structures are shown side-by-side, each surrounded by brackets. The left structure shows the symbol M with a superscripted two positive sign. The right shows the symbol X surrounded by four lone pairs of electrons with a superscripted two negative sign outside of the brackets.">
